{"tid":472051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有科大畢業生背向校監林鄭月娥　奏國歌期間有疑似噓聲","createTime":"2017-11-17T23:50:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T00:37:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f80656c3e83eb6f9a0acb18046efde8b7a22c86","tid":472051,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:50:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365448-20171117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365448-20171117.htm&d=Fy44ZujKm9oT4Thc8K%2FcJf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=57526b8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1365448-20171117.htm&h=b24683c9\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1365448-20171117.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1365448_1_20171117191846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1365448_1_20171117191846.jpg&h=00580dd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n身兼科技大學當然校監的行政長官林鄭月娥，下午出席科大學位頒授典禮。<br />\n<br />\n在頒授工學院本科生學位期間，有數名畢業生只向校長陳繁昌以及工學院院長鞠躬，未有停步向林鄭月娥鞠躬；亦有畢業生背向林鄭月娥，並只向觀眾席鞠躬，但大部分畢業生都有分別向三人鞠躬。<br />\n<br />\n典禮期間，奏完國歌後，現場有人發出疑似噓聲。"},{"pid":"dac352d7dd8552122cfe261bce17f601b5f0cda5","tid":472051,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:53:07.000Z","msg":"普遍化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2744d99fe7864cde75c85885fdd64aea5669e999","tid":472051,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:56:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>普遍化<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n已經發展到, 唔止係球場, 係全港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2014/new/oct/2/images/bigPic/400_400/157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn